code: public void setContext(SocketChannelContext context) {     if (contextSet.compareAndSet(false, true)) {         this.context = context.     } else {         throw new IllegalStateException("Context on this channel were already set. It should only be once.").     } }

@Override public InetSocketAddress getLocalAddress() {     if (localAddress == null) {         localAddress = (InetSocketAddress) socketChannel.socket().getLocalSocketAddress().     }     return localAddress. }
public void addConnectListener(BiConsumer<Void, Exception> listener) {     context.addConnectListener(listener). }
@Override public String toString() {     return "NioSocketChannel{" + "localAddress=" + getLocalAddress() + ", remoteAddress=" + remoteAddress + '}'. }
